        FROM [Products] AS [p4]
        INNER JOIN [Subcategories] AS [p.Subcategory4] ON [p4].[SubcategoryID] = [p.Subcategory4].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [p.Category4] ON [p4].[CategoryID] = [p.Category4].[Id]
    ) AS [t3] ON [p.Subcategory.FilterOptions0].[SubcategoryID] = [t3].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [p.Subcategory.FilterOptions.Values].[FilterOptionID] = [t4].[Id]
ORDER BY [t4].[Id0], [t4].[Id1], [t4].[Id2], [t4].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
